members.doc:
A list of colors to be used in the icon. In order for the colors to be
applied, the SVG markup must contain the attributes 'data-color="[Color
Index]""'. The applied color on that element will be the index modulo the
length of the colors list.

members.doc:
Paint the icon element as a mirror image of isself vertically and/or
horizontally

members.doc:
A float value between 0-1. null value will be considered as 1 (full
opacity)

members.doc: Defines a rotation for the letter. 0 by default

members.name: scale
members.doc:
Scales the letter. The origin of the scale is located at: horizontally -
Center of the letter, Vertically - base line of the letter.

members.name: translate
members.doc:
Defines a movement vector for the letter *relative* to it's original
position. By default it is { x: 0, y: 0}

members.name: curve
members.doc:
Curves the text according to an angle: 0 - means straight line (regular),
360 - Text appears as a full circle.

members.name: custom
members.doc: Custom transformation for each letter defined by the user.

members.doc: Center coordinate of the circle of the radial gradient

members.doc: Defined the start point of the radial gradient start. The stop defined at the 0% location will be mapped to that point.

members.doc: Radius from the center point defining the outer perimeter of the gradient. The 100% of the last stop is mapped to that perimiter.

members.name: spreadMethod
members.doc: Determines how a shape is filled beyond the defined edges of a gradient

members.doc: List of gradient colors and their positions.

members.doc:
Applies only on shape of type SQUARE. It is the percentage of the roundness
ranges between 0 to 50%. (50% means an oval rectangle)

members.name: roundCornerUnit
members.doc:
Determines how the corner radius value is calculated on the element
(Default is PERCENT)

members.doc: Color of the border of the shape.

members.name: strokeWidthUnit

Determines how the Stroke value is calculated on the element
(Default is PIXELS)

opacity)
